    &nbsp;&nbsp;✓ **Subsidy flip**: Public funds support *only* regenerative production of diverse, whole foods—*not* corn/soy/sugar for feed or junk food.  
    &nbsp;&nbsp;✓ **Universal access**: No one pays >10% of income for a nutritious, culturally resonant diet (achieved via local food trusts + true cost pricing).  
- **Why it works**: Ends the paradox of obesity amid malnutrition. Food becomes a expression of place and care—not a vector for corporate profit or ecological theft.  

