> **If you see a group the ESF endangers—tell me how.** Not to defend the framework, but to sharpen it. Because the only thing more dangerous than a flawed framework is one that refuses to see its flaws.  
>   
> *Where would you add, challenge, or rebuild this critique?* This framework only grows in the soil of dissent.

