*Who they are*: Silicon Valley venture capitalists, AI ethicists (e.g., from Google/DeepMind), transhumanist thinkers, and data-mining conglomerates (Meta, Alphabet, Palantir)—groups that believe technology can solve any problem *without* systemic change.  

**Their Most Effective Argument**:  
