- **It has real power**: These actors control capital, data, legislation, and global institutions—not just protests or op-eds.  
- **Historical precedent wins**: This is how the tobacco industry delayed regulation for 50 years by demanding "more proof," and how fossil fuel lobbies neutered Kyoto Protocol.  

