| Conflict resolution used restorative circles only. | Added **algorithmic accountability forums**, **witnessing‑and‑transition‑dignity audits**, and **formal impact assessments** (Sentience, Carnism/Zoological Witchcraft, Witnessing, Transition Dignity, True‑Cost). |
| Technology guardrails were purpose/access/reversibility/boundary/kinship. | Added **Sentience Gate**, **Health‑Impact Test**, **Nutritional Adequacy Test**, **True‑Cost test**, **Carnism/Zoological Witchcraft test**, **Witnessing/Transition Dignity test** – a full nine‑gate filter that must be cleared before any innovation proceeds. |
